923
00:37:21,033 --> 00:37:23,434
(laughs cynically)

924
00:37:30,527 --> 00:37:33,394
(inhales deeply)

925
00:37:33,396 --> 00:37:35,530
(exhales)

926
00:37:37,067 --> 00:37:38,566
Lovely.

927
00:37:45,722 --> 00:37:47,343
I knew you'd save yourself.

928
00:37:49,246 --> 00:37:51,479
