out of that burning car.

942
00:38:28,385 --> 00:38:32,120
And I certainly don't have one now.

943
00:38:33,961 --> 00:38:36,895
You'll understand soon enough.

944
00:38:53,143 --> 00:38:54,809
Where is he?

945
00:38:54,811 --> 00:38:57,412
