00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:19,127
- Happy?
- Yeah.

971
00:40:19,129 --> 00:40:22,363
The detective and I... Sorry...

972
00:40:22,365 --> 00:40:24,966
Chloe and I are real.

973
00:40:24,968 --> 00:40:27,602
I mean, I didn't think it could happen,

974
